desc_long							评测						“The pure, palpable joy of discovery is childlike in the best way.”9.2 – Apps Zoom“I didn't realize it until playing Ephemerid, but there isn't nearly enough crunchy guitar in rhythm games.”Joystiq“A unique blend of music and adventure, Ephemerid has in its core the original soundtracks with strong rhythm and beats. Combined with the artistic world, the game immerses you into a refreshing journey into a world of wonder and charm.”92% – Gameoos												关于这款游戏							2015 IGF Winner: Excellence in AudioEphemerid is a rock fairy tale about a paper mayfly.Lean back, relax and enjoy it as a whole, as you would a favorite album. Ephemerid is part rhythm game, part point-and-click adventure, and part rock opera.KEY FEATURESEphemerid’s beating heart is its original soundtrack, rock guitar with a classical flair.The world of Ephemerid is faithfully handcrafted out of cut paper, glass, and paint.Each setting introduces intuitive challenges which play in harmony with the music.ACCOLADES2015 IGF Winner: Excellence in Audio2014 SXSW Gamer's Voice Finalist2014 BIG Festival Finalist2013 IndieCade Finalist2013 Captivate Finalist						
